import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row, Card } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Slider from '../src/Components/Slider'

export const Home = () => {
    return(
        <>
        <Slider/>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Card style = {{width: '18em'}}>
                    <Card.Img variant='top' />
                     
                </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container> 
        </>
    )
}
